        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
              <a class="post-title-link" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/324.html" itemprop="url">
                CentOS 下 Docker、Docker-Compose 的安装              </a>          
        </h1>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-time">
          发表于
          <time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2016-06-01T21:58:00+08:00" content="1616-06-01">
            2016-06-01          </time>
        </span>
        <span class="post-category" >
            &nbsp; | &nbsp; 分类于
              <span itemprop="about" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Thing">
                <a href="https://www.tomey.me/category/linux/">Linux 技术</a>              </span>
       </span>
       <span class="post-comments-count">
                &nbsp; | &nbsp;
                            <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/324.html#comments">暂无评论</a>
                     </span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">
        <h4>安装前检查</h4>
<p>检查系统内核，并确保内核版本在 3.1以上。</p>
<blockquote>
<p># uname -r<br />
3.10.0-229.el7.x86_64</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="more"><a href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/324.html" title="CentOS 下 Docker、Docker-Compose 的安装">阅读全文 »</a></p>    </div>

