  <article class="post post-type-normal " itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
    <header class="post-header">
        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
              <a class="post-title-link" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/326.html" itemprop="url">
                CentOS 内核升级              </a>          
        </h1>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-time">
          发表于
          <time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2016-05-31T09:25:00+08:00" content="1616-05-31">
            2016-05-31          </time>
        </span>
        <span class="post-category" >
            &nbsp; | &nbsp; 分类于
              <span itemprop="about" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Thing">
                <a href="https://www.tomey.me/category/linux/">Linux 技术</a>              </span>
       </span>
       <span class="post-comments-count">
                &nbsp; | &nbsp;
                            <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/326.html#comments">暂无评论</a>
                     </span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">
        <h4>配置 yum 源地址</h4>
<p>vim /etc/yum.repos.d/kernel.repo</p>
<blockquote>
<p>[kernel-update]<br />
name=kernel-update<br />
baseurl=http://elrepo.org/linux/kernel/el$releasever/$basearch/<br />
gpgcheck=0</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="more"><a href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/326.html" title="CentOS 内核升级">阅读全文 »</a></p>    </div>

