  <article class="post post-type-normal " itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
    <header class="post-header">
        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
              <a class="post-title-link" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/317.html" itemprop="url">
                Centos 下安装 Squid 透明代理              </a>          
        </h1>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-time">
          发表于
          <time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2016-05-27T16:33:00+08:00" content="1616-05-27">
            2016-05-27          </time>
        </span>
        <span class="post-category" >
            &nbsp; | &nbsp; 分类于
              <span itemprop="about" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Thing">
                <a href="https://www.tomey.me/category/linux/">Linux 技术</a>              </span>
       </span>
       <span class="post-comments-count">
                &nbsp; | &nbsp;
                            <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/317.html#comments">暂无评论</a>
                     </span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">
        <p>相关介绍:<br />
Linux代理软件squid可以实现正向、反向代理，我们用正向代理的功能来实现多人上网，用反向代理来提高WEB的响应能力。反向代理的维护复杂得多，这篇小文只介绍正向代理部分，起因也是多人通过Linux主机共享上网。</p>
<p class="more"><a href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/317.html" title="Centos 下安装 Squid 透明代理">阅读全文 »</a></p>    </div>

