  <article class="post post-type-normal " itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
    <header class="post-header">
        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
              <a class="post-title-link" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/306.html" itemprop="url">
                Nginx 防止被恶意压力测试方法              </a>          
        </h1>
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-time">
          发表于
          <time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2016-05-21T19:03:00+08:00" content="1616-05-21">
            2016-05-21          </time>
        </span>
        <span class="post-category" >
            &nbsp; | &nbsp; 分类于
              <span itemprop="about" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Thing">
                <a href="https://www.tomey.me/category/linux/">Linux 技术</a>              </span>
       </span>
       <span class="post-comments-count">
                &nbsp; | &nbsp;
                            <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/306.html#comments">暂无评论</a>
                     </span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">
        <p>因为网站没有做连接数限制，所以只要有人使用 ab siege 等一些压力测试工具来模拟并发压服务器，服务器就很容易被压垮。</p>
<p>可以参考官方文档的配置方法：<a href="http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_limit_conn_module.html" target="_bleak"> http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_limit_conn_module.html </a></p>
<p class="more"><a href="https://www.tomey.me/blog/306.html" title="Nginx 防止被恶意压力测试方法">阅读全文 »</a></p>    </div>

    <footer class="post-footer">

        <div class="post-eof"></div>
      
